INNER JOIN `Category` AS `c` ON `p`.`CategoryId` = `c`.`Id`

    SELECT `p0`.`ProductId`, `p0`.`SupplierId`, `p0`.`Date`, `p0`.`SupplyPrice`, `s`.`SupplierId` AS `SupplierId0`, `s`.`CNPJ`, `s`.`ContactPerson`, `s`.`DayToPay`, `s`.`Email`, `s`.`Name`, `s`.`Phone`, `s`.`ShippingValue`, `s`.`SupplierType`, `s`.`Website`
    FROM `ProductSupplier` AS `p0`
    INNER JOIN `Supplier` AS `s` ON `p0`.`SupplierId` = `s`.`SupplierId`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`Id` = `t`.`ProductId`
WHERE `p`.`Name` LIKE @__Format_1
ORDER BY `p`.`Id`, `d`.`Id`, `c`.`Id`, `t`.`ProductId`, `t`.`SupplierId`

        LEFT JOIN Product AS p ON c.Id == p.CategoryId

    False,

SELECT `p`.`Id`, `p`.`AcquisitionCost`, `p`.`BarCode`, `p`.`CategoryId`, `p`.`DepartmentId`, `p`.`Description`, `p`.`ImageUrl`, `p`.`InventoryCost`, `p`.`InventoryQuantity`, `p`.`InventoryUnitMeas`, `p`.`MinimumInventoryQuantity`, `p`.`Name`, `p`.`Price`, `d`.`Id`, `d`.`Address`, `d`.`CNPJ`, `d`.`Name`, `c`.`Id`, `c`.`DepartmentId`, `c`.`Description`, `c`.`Name`, `t`.`ProductId`, `t`.`SupplierId`, `t`.`Date`, `t`.`SupplyPrice`, `t`.`SupplierId0`, `t`.`CNPJ`, `t`.`ContactPerson`, `t`.`DayToPay`, `t`.`Email`, `t`.`Name`, `t`.`Phone`, `t`.`ShippingValue`, `t`.`SupplierType`, `t`.`Website`
FROM `Product` AS `p`
INNER JOIN `Department` AS `d` ON `p`.`DepartmentId` = `d`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Category` AS `c` ON `p`.`CategoryId` = `c`.`Id`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p0`.`ProductId`, `p0`.`SupplierId`, `p0`.`Date`, `p0`.`SupplyPrice`, `s`.`SupplierId` AS `SupplierId0`, `s`.`CNPJ`, `s`.`ContactPerson`, `s`.`DayToPay`, `s`.`Email`, `s`.`Name`, `s`.`Phone`, `s`.`ShippingValue`, `s`.`SupplierType`, `s`.`Website`

    INNER JOIN `Supplier` AS `s` ON `p0`.`SupplierId` = `s`.`SupplierId`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`Id` = `t`.`ProductId`
WHERE `p`.`Name` LIKE @__Format_1
ORDER BY `p`.`Id`, `d`.`Id`, `c`.`Id`, `t`.`ProductId`, `t`.`SupplierId`

SELECT `p`.`Id`, `p`.`AcquisitionCost`, `p`.`BarCode`, `p`.`CategoryId`, `p`.`DepartmentId`, `p`.`Description`, `p`.`ImageUrl`, `p`.`InventoryCost`, `p`.`InventoryQuantity`, `p`.`InventoryUnitMeas`, `p`.`MinimumInventoryQuantity`, `p`.`Name`, `p`.`Price`, `d`.`Id`, `d`.`Address`, `d`.`CNPJ`, `d`.`Name`, `c`.`Id`, `c`.`DepartmentId`, `c`.`Description`, `c`.`Name`, `t`.`ProductId`, `t`.`SupplierId`, `t`.`Date`, `t`.`SupplyPrice`, `t`.`SupplierId0`, `t`.`CNPJ`, `t`.`ContactPerson`, `t`.`DayToPay`, `t`.`Email`, `t`.`Name`, `t`.`Phone`, `t`.`ShippingValue`, `t`.`SupplierType`, `t`.`Website`
FROM `Product` AS `p`
INNER JOIN `Department` AS `d` ON `p`.`DepartmentId` = `d`.`Id`

        FROM Product AS p
        INNER JOIN Department AS d ON p.DepartmentId == d.Id
        INNER JOIN Category AS c ON p.CategoryId == c.Id
        LEFT JOIN

            SELECT p0.ProductId, p0.SupplierId, p0.Date, p0.SupplyPrice, s.SupplierId AS SupplierId0, s.CNPJ, s.ContactPerson, s.DayToPay, s.Email, s.Name, s.Phone, s.ShippingValue, s.SupplierType, s.Website
